  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-width: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://athomewithgrowingold.com/wp-content/uploads/home-slides-081.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\"><img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/shetuan/f24b959f-a79e-4b79-a9c0-9f8a488c12f8.jpg\" /><span>&nbsp;</span></a><span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tRefer<br />\n\tTo refer means to point towards a source of information. What or who is referring? How is the action done? What will be the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They referred to their notes... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) refer to the source document<br />\n\t2) refer to the records<br />\n\t3) refer a friend<br />\n\t4) refer the case to a higher court<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWolfe had the impression that the model did not like him from the get-go. That stunning face, Wolfe could not deny that, seemed to be always smirking at him. Of course, that could just be how the model smiled, but then again, Wolfe had seen him show a completely different smile to other people and in his photoshoots. Ah, whatever, focus Wolfe, focus! &ldquo;Very well, what have you been up to lately?&rdquo; Wolfe continued with his questions. &ldquo;Depends on what you are referring to, I have been kept quite busy lately.&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/1710451443292/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p983841/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p983841\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1012535/\">双语美文：你尽力了，但仍然会出问题</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1019530/\">国产修图app火了：老外表示我好美！爱死了！ </a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1012395/\">双语美